{"type":"message","id":"37dd22af","parentId":"6d712adf","timestamp":"2026-03-07T01:03:41.326Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_019rp6kCBD5sQtmbP74aXJdo","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/usr/local/Cellar/node@22/22.22.0_1/bin/qmd\nqmd 1.0.7\nUsage:\n  qmd collection add [path] --name <name> --mask <pattern>  - Create/index collection\n  qmd collection list           - List all collections with details\n  qmd collection remove <name>  - Remove a collection by name\n  qmd collection rename <old> <new>  - Rename a collection\n  qmd ls [collection[/path]]    - List collections or files in a collection\n  qmd context add [path] \"text\" - Add context for path (defaults to current dir)\n  qmd context list              - List all contexts\n  qmd context rm <path>         - Remove context\n  qmd get <file>[:line] [-l N] [--from N]  - Get document (optionally from line, max N lines)\n  qmd multi-get <pattern> [-l N] [--max-bytes N]  - Get multiple docs by glob or comma-separated list\n  qmd status                    - Show index status and collections\n  qmd update [--pull]           - Re-index all collections (--pull: git pull first)\n  qmd embed [-f]                - Create vector embeddings (900 tokens/chunk, 15% overlap)\n  qmd cleanup                   - Remove cache and orphaned data, vacuum DB\n  qmd query <query>             - Search with query expansion + reranking (recommended)\n  qmd search <query>            - Full-text keyword search (BM25, no LLM)\n  qmd vsearch <query>           - Vector similarity search (no reranking)\n  qmd mcp                       - Start MCP server (stdio transport)\n  qmd mcp --http [--port N]     - Start MCP server (HTTP transport, default port 8181)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1648,"aggregated":"/usr/local/Cellar/node@22/22.22.0_1/bin/qmd\nqmd 1.0.7\nUsage:\n  qmd collection add [path] --name <name> --mask <pattern>  - Create/index collection\n  qmd collection list