{"type":"message","id":"60c16dbe","parentId":"8e5f4940","timestamp":"2026-03-07T01:05:01.115Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The memory status shows it's using a different store path: `~/.openclaw/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache/qmd/index.sqlite` (agent-specific), while earlier the QMD was using `~/.cache/qmd/index.sqlite` (global). \n\nThe `memory_search` tool must be looking for a collection in the agent-specific QMD store, not the global one. And the collection name is likely different too.\n\nLet me check the agent-specific QMD store and see what collections exist there.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01JHTimauKa43XEoYBMW61fF","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"XDG_CACHE_HOME=~/.openclaw/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache qmd collection list 2>&1; echo \"---\"; XDG_CACHE_HOME=~/.openclaw/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache qmd status 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":264,"cacheRead":23906,"cacheWrite":184,"totalTokens":24355,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00396,"cacheRead":0.0071718,"cacheWrite":0.00069,"total":0.0118248}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772845494342}}
{"type":"message","id":"683f9224","parentId":"60c16dbe","timestamp":"2026-03-07T01:05:02.690Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01JHTimauKa43XEoYBMW61fF","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Collections (2):\n\nworkspace (qmd://workspace/)\n  Pattern:  **/*.md\n  Files:    0\n  Updated:  0s ago\n\nmemory (qmd://memory/)\n  Pattern:  **/*.md\n  Files:    0\n  Updated:  0s ago\n\n---\nQMD Status\n\nIndex: /Users/aiagnet/.openclaw/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache/qmd/index.sqlite\nSize:  3.7 MB\n\nDocuments\n  Total:    29 files indexed\n  Vectors:  27 embedded\n  Pending:  3 need embedding (run 'qmd embed')\n  Updated:  4m ago\n\nCollections\n  workspace (qmd://workspace/)\n    Pattern:  **/*.md\n    Files:    0 (updated never)\n  memory (qmd://memory/)\n    Pattern:  **/*.md\n    Files:    0 (updated never)\n\nExamples\n  # List files in a collection\n  qmd ls workspace\n  # Get a document\n  qmd get qmd://workspace/path/to/file.md\n  # Search within a collection\n  qmd search \"query\" -c workspace\n\nModels\n  Embedding:   https://huggingface.co/ggml-org/embeddinggemma-300M-GGUF\n  Reranking:   https://huggingface.co/ggml-org/Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B-Q8_0-GGUF\n  Generation:  https://huggingface.co/tobil/qmd-query-expansion-1.7B-gguf\n\nDevice\n  GPU:      none (running on CPU — models will be slow)\n  Tip: Install CUDA, Vulkan, or Metal support for GPU acceleration.\n  CPU:      2 math cores"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1571,"aggregated":"Collections (2):\n\nworkspace (qmd://workspace/)\n  Pattern:  **/*.md\n  Files:    0\n  Updated:  0s ago\n\nmemory (qmd://memory/)\n  Pattern:  **/*.md\n  Files:    0\n  Updated:  0s ago\n\n---\nQMD Status\n\nIndex: /Users/aiagnet/.openclaw/agents/main/qmd/xdg-cache/qmd/index.sqlite\nSize:  3.7 MB\n\nDocuments\n  Total:    29 files indexed\n  Vectors:  27 embedded\n  Pending:  3 need embedding (run 'qmd embed')\n  Updated:  4m ago\n\nCollections\n  workspace (qmd://workspace/)\n    Pattern:  **/*.md\n    Files:    0 (updated never)\n  memory (qmd://memory/)\n    Pattern:  **/*.md\n    Files:    0 (updated never)\n\nExamples\n  # List files in a collection\n  qmd ls workspace\n  # Get a document\n  qmd get qmd://workspace/path/to/file.md\n  # Search within a collection\n  qmd search \"query\" -c workspace\n\nModels\n  Embedding:   https://huggingface.co/ggml-org/embeddinggemma-300M-GGUF\n  Reranking:   https://huggingface.co/ggml-org/Qwen3-Reranker-0.6B-Q8_0-GGUF\n  Generation:  https://huggingface.co/tobil/qmd-query-expansion-1.7B-gguf\n\nDevice\n  GPU:      none (running on CPU — models will be slow)\n  Tip: Install CUDA, Vulkan, or Metal support for GPU acceleration.\n  CPU:      2 math cores","cwd":"/Users/aiagnet/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772845502688}}
{"type":"message","id":"c9c76630","parentId":"683f9224","timestamp":"2026-03-07T01:05:06.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the agent-specific QMD store has collections \"workspace\" and \"memory\", not \"memory-dir-main\". The `memory_search` tool is failing because it's looking for `memory-dir-main` which doesn't exist in the agent-specific QMD store.\n\nLet me try to run the memory_search with openclaw CLI to see what it does.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_017V65oZB8yJmsXLQr2cYmnA","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw memory search \"pink elephant\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":158,"cacheRead":24090,"cacheWrite":709,"totalTokens":24958,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.00237,"cacheRead":0.007227,"cacheWrite":0.00265875,"total":0.01225875}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772845502690}}
